rows.label: qst630201_msg0002
rows.name: When will you come back to me...?

rows.label: qst630201_msg0003
rows.name: Huh? What stroke of fate is this?

rows.label: qst630201_msg0004
rows.name:
Hræsvelgr Mercenaries, come to chat
to me? Well I never...

rows.label: qst630201_msg0005
rows.name:
It's Lhagen, my daughter...
I've not seen or heard from her
ever since she left for Avaritia...

rows.label: qst630201_msg0008
rows.name:
I would expect no less from the famed
Hræsvelgr group... You promise me you'll
reunite me with my little girl?

rows.label: qst630201_msg0009
rows.name: I can think of no better news...

rows.label: qst630201_msg0010
rows.name:
My beloved, strange little donut said
she only wanted to check on the latest
in millinery... Millinery means "hats".

rows.label: qst630201_msg0011
rows.name: I really hope you can find her soon...
